Comment: 0,0:00:00.10,0:00:00.10,Comment,,0,0,0,,——Text——
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.73,0:00:03.90,Default,,0,0,0,,「血潮」不見了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.69,0:00:07.57,Default,,0,0,0,,漏了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.94,0:00:08.73,Default,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.32,0:00:11.57,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼一直沒有發現呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.82,0:00:13.49,Default,,0,0,0,,佐佐木女士
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.99,0:00:16.99,Default,,0,0,0,,以防萬一  請確認下「用例採集卡」
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.28,0:00:18.03,Default,,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.75,0:00:28.17,Default,,0,0,0,,採集卡裡確實有「血潮」
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.13,0:00:33.51,Default,,0,0,0,,調整行數把「血潮」加進去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.55,0:00:38.18,Default,,0,0,0,,問題在於是否還有其餘遺漏
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.69,0:00:45.69,Default,,0,0,0,,現在停下一切手頭工作
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.31,0:00:48.40,Default,,0,0,0,,從頭核對四校稿
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.82,0:00:53.95,Default,,0,0,0,,把24萬個詞條重新核對一遍吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.69,0:02:31.82,Default,,0,0,0,,這次交給大家的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.24,0:02:35.53,Default,,0,0,0,,攸關『大渡海』的成敗  極為重要
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.24,0:02:38.62,Default,,0,0,0,,希望大家做好準備  認真對待
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.95,0:02:41.45,Default,,0,0,0,,各位
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.87,0:02:46.08,Default,,0,0,0,,這對你們來說會是相當艱辛的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.75,0:02:49.09,Default,,0,0,0,,但是  無論花費多少時間
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.67,0:02:52.13,Default,,0,0,0,,都非完成不可
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.17,0:02:55.30,Default,,0,0,0,,為了不讓『大渡海』這艘船出現破洞
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.01,0:02:58.14,Default,,0,0,0,,請務必助我們一臂之力
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.48,0:03:05.69,Default,,0,0,0,,開始工作吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.65,0:03:14.53,Default,,0,0,0,,我們要確認索引列表裡的詞條
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.82,0:03:17.66,Default,,0,0,0,,是否出現在校樣稿中
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.95,0:03:19.07,Default,,0,0,0,,好的  我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.30,0:03:25.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn方正细雅宋_GBK\fs35\b0\bord0\pos(393.334,167.333)\fad(0,1680)\c&H282B26&}進展表
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.30,0:03:25.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs30\an7\bord0\fad(0,1680)\c&H5A5B58&\pos(740,0)}工作要點\N{\fs25}清楚的地方請馬上詢問荒木  岸邊或佐佐木\N即便讀音相同  也要認真核對每個漢字\N疲勞時注意力下降\N漏看的詞會變多\N請及時休息
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.38,0:03:32.84,Default,,0,0,0,,你看得好快
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.63,0:03:34.96,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼提高效率啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.42,0:03:37.26,Default,,0,0,0,,吵死了  別和我說話
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.02,0:03:46.43,Default,,0,0,0,,我來接
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.31,0:03:50.77,Default,,0,0,0,,您好  這裡是玄武書房辭典編輯部
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.48,0:03:52.52,Default,,0,0,0,,啊  您好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.78,0:03:57.32,Default,,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.65,0:03:59.03,Default,,0,0,0,,請稍等
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.24,0:04:01.91,Default,,0,0,0,,馬締先生
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.49,0:04:03.03,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.66,0:04:05.70,Default,,0,0,0,,松本老師的妻子打來的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.21,0:04:09.37,Default,,0,0,0,,老師住院了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.79,0:04:11.88,Default,,0,0,0,,哪一家醫院
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.22,0:04:27.52,Default,,0,0,0,,荒木先生正在詢問老師的病房號
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.23,0:04:32.77,Default,,0,0,0,,老師最近瘦了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.06,0:04:33.46,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.90,0:04:35.57,Default,,0,0,0,,我聽說了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.07,0:04:38.61,Default,,0,0,0,,你們最近招了很多兼職人員重新核對四校稿
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.49,0:04:39.95,Default,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.95,0:04:41.61,Default,,0,0,0,,馬締
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.66,0:04:43.62,Default,,0,0,0,,沒問題吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.91,0:04:46.66,Default,,0,0,0,,沒問題
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.67,0:04:51.37,Default,,0,0,0,,也是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.88,0:04:54.79,Comment,,0,0,0,,在203病房
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.13,0:04:57.92,Comment,,0,0,0,,下了電梯往左手邊走
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.84,0:05:00.72,Comment,,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.71,0:04:54.84,Default,,0,0,0,,啊  老師知道這事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.13,0:04:55.67,Default,,0,0,0,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.09,0:04:57.80,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯  還是不要告訴他老人家為好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.42,0:05:01.30,Default,,0,0,0,,別讓他過度擔心了  對身體不好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.63,0:05:02.09,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.64,0:05:03.93,Default,,0,0,0,,好了  我們走
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.10,0:05:10.64,Default,,0,0,0,,請進
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.02,0:05:12.19,Default,,0,0,0,,打擾了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.78,0:05:20.11,Default,,0,0,0,,看看誰來了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.40,0:05:21.36,Default,,0,0,0,,老師
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.86,0:05:24.49,Default,,0,0,0,,真是抱歉  勞煩你們百忙之中來探病
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.03,0:05:26.37,Default,,0,0,0,,久疏問候
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.70,0:05:28.91,Default,,0,0,0,,這是老師喜歡的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.54,0:05:33.67,Default,,0,0,0,,讓你們費心了  非常感謝
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.79,0:05:36.96,Default,,0,0,0,,你們特意跑來看我  真是過意不去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.25,0:05:39.63,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼會  您身體如何
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.92,0:05:42.51,Default,,0,0,0,,如你所見
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.93,0:05:47.60,Default,,0,0,0,,老師  您可不能勉強自己啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.06,0:05:51.89,Default,,0,0,0,,想必是內人慌亂之下聯絡了你們
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.02,0:05:55.10,Default,,0,0,0,,太小題大做了  不過是住院檢查罷了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.81,0:05:57.27,Default,,0,0,0,,這是個好機會
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.48,0:05:59.57,Default,,0,0,0,,請好好休養身子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.03,0:06:03.53,Default,,0,0,0,,偏偏在這『大渡海』即將完成的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.53,0:06:06.32,Default,,0,0,0,,我還真是沒用
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.04,0:06:11.58,Default,,0,0,0,,『大渡海』的進度如何
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.79,0:06:12.33,Default,,0,0,0,,啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.58,0:06:13.91,Default,,0,0,0,,順利極了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.46,0:06:16.83,Default,,0,0,0,,裝幀設計也快完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.84,0:06:18.38,Default,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.67,0:06:21.67,Default,,0,0,0,,哦  這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.92,0:06:23.92,Default,,0,0,0,,真是讓人期待啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.63,0:06:26.47,Default,,0,0,0,,不過話說回來  老師啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.80,0:06:28.93,Default,,0,0,0,,您剛住院還不忘採集用例
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.10,0:06:30.31,Default,,0,0,0,,我都被您嚇到了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.93,0:06:33.23,Default,,0,0,0,,這已經是我生活的一部分了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.64,0:06:38.40,Default,,0,0,0,,不愧是老師  希望能早日拜讀
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.48,0:06:42.94,Default,,0,0,0,,我可遇到了些頗有意思的詞語
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.99,0:06:48.62,Default,,0,0,0,,老師要檢查多久
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.12,0:06:51.16,Default,,0,0,0,,具體我也不清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.87,0:06:55.04,Default,,0,0,0,,我也沒聽說要住院多少天
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.12,0:06:56.12,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.17,0:06:59.92,Default,,0,0,0,,不過  老師的臉色還不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.17,0:07:04.05,Default,,0,0,0,,想必稍微休息幾天  身子就能恢復了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.26,0:07:06.88,Default,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.14,0:07:12.89,Default,,0,0,0,,正如荒木先生所說
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.06,0:07:15.14,Default,,0,0,0,,這也許正是個好機會
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.52,0:07:20.15,Default,,0,0,0,,松本還是老樣子  不注意休息
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.36,0:07:26.53,Default,,0,0,0,,也請各位無需掛心  專心工作吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.24,0:07:30.53,Default,,0,0,0,,我也非常期待『大渡海』完成
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.24,0:07:32.33,Default,,0,0,0,,非常感謝
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.74,0:07:34.95,Default,,0,0,0,,如果有任何情況
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.33,0:07:35.83,Default,,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.50,0:07:39.04,Default,,0,0,0,,我會聯絡你們的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.21,0:07:41.88,Default,,0,0,0,,那就拜託您了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.42,0:07:43.80,Default,,0,0,0,,請多多保重
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.80,0:08:12.51,Default,,0,0,0,,沒問題
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.18,0:08:14.68,Default,,0,0,0,,這些接下來就交給你了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.47,0:08:17.47,Default,,0,0,0,,「か」行還剩這麼多啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.02,0:08:20.14,Default,,0,0,0,,別擔心  我們進展很順利
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.10,0:08:23.65,Default,,0,0,0,,不過  我總覺得目標遙遙無期
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.06,0:08:26.90,Default,,0,0,0,,別這麼說  加油吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.94,0:08:28.44,Default,,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.80,0:08:53.97,Default,,0,0,0,,空氣力學
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.14,0:08:54.93,Default,,0,0,0,,氣冷
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.30,0:08:56.18,Default,,0,0,0,,空氣吉他
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.35,0:08:57.56,Default,,0,0,0,,空氣計劃
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.64,0:08:58.35,Default,,0,0,0,,空氣質量
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.77,0:08:59.43,Default,,0,0,0,,空氣性
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.93,0:09:01.02,Default,,0,0,0,,空氣調節
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.06,0:09:02.10,Default,,0,0,0,,空氣傳染
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.48,0:09:03.23,Default,,0,0,0,,空虛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.48,0:09:04.40,Default,,0,0,0,,空御
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.73,0:09:05.52,Default,,0,0,0,,寓所
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.81,0:09:06.57,Default,,0,0,0,,空教
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.94,0:09:08.11,Default,,0,0,0,,空氣揚水筒
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.48,0:09:09.11,Default,,0,0,0,,偶因
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.57,0:09:10.28,Default,,0,0,0,,呼嚕呼嚕
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.84,0:10:10.80,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉  抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.80,0:10:11.46,Default,,0,0,0,,大家辛苦啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.01,0:10:13.26,Default,,0,0,0,,我帶慰問品來了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.76,0:10:15.55,Default,,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.80,0:10:16.76,Default,,0,0,0,,大家快來吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.68,0:10:19.35,Default,,0,0,0,,佐佐木姐也快來吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.83,0:10:46.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord0\c&H434A49&\fax-0.2\frz356.4\pos(773,530)}嚴禁穿鞋入內!!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.79,0:10:51.84,Default,,0,0,0,,不行了  腦子一團漿糊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.17,0:10:54.38,Default,,0,0,0,,來  稍微休息一會兒吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.59,0:10:55.42,Default,,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.55,0:10:56.63,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼樣  舒服嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.25,0:11:37.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&H242222&\fs30\bord0\pos(990,86)}目標完工!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.25,0:11:37.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&H3E443F&\fs30\bord0\frz353.1\pos(537.333,343.333)}工作注意事項
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.25,0:11:37.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&H424545&\fs30\bord0\pos(573,614.667)\frz341.4}不清楚的地方請馬上詢問荒木\N岸邊或佐佐木
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.22,0:11:45.14,Default,,0,0,0,,拿衣服來洗過的人請按順序過來認領
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.64,0:11:47.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&H3E443F&\fs40\fsp10\bord0\pos(786,269)\frz13.05}執勤表
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.81,0:11:46.93,Default,,0,0,0,,來了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.44,0:11:49.98,Default,,0,0,0,,我說你們啊  工作如何
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.40,0:11:53.02,Default,,0,0,0,,速度變快了超多
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.36,0:11:54.32,Default,,0,0,0,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.48,0:11:56.40,Default,,0,0,0,,大家的效率都提高了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.90,0:11:58.15,Default,,0,0,0,,是嘛  是嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.36,0:11:59.11,Default,,0,0,0,,非常好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.53,0:12:00.95,Default,,0,0,0,,那允許你們加麵
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.49,0:12:03.70,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.87,0:12:49.54,Default,,0,0,0,,馬締
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.21,0:12:53.13,Default,,0,0,0,,世界和語言正在消失
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.92,0:12:54.71,Default,,0,0,0,,馬締
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.21,0:12:55.92,Default,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.80,0:13:00.59,Default,,0,0,0,,馬締
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.39,0:13:04.55,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.85,0:13:08.06,Default,,0,0,0,,大家看上去都已經到極限了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.97,0:13:11.48,Default,,0,0,0,,有些人好幾天都沒回家了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.14,0:13:14.19,Default,,0,0,0,,繼續工作效率也只會越來越低
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.98,0:13:15.77,Default,,0,0,0,,確實
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.69,0:13:19.53,Default,,0,0,0,,今天就讓大家回家好好休息吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.44,0:13:22.45,Default,,0,0,0,,就這麼辦吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.07,0:13:59.82,Default,,0,0,0,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.54,0:14:15.96,Default,,0,0,0,,虎雄  早安
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.50,0:14:21.42,Default,,0,0,0,,歡迎回來
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.01,0:14:25.68,Default,,0,0,0,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.36,0:14:41.36,Default,,0,0,0,,久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.95,0:14:56.25,Default,,0,0,0,,好久沒吃到你做的飯了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.12,0:14:58.50,Default,,0,0,0,,你有好好吃飯嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.92,0:14:59.42,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.34,0:15:02.55,Default,,0,0,0,,不好好吃飯的話  身體會扛不住的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.96,0:15:03.55,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.71,0:15:06.17,Default,,0,0,0,,還有好多事要做
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.97,0:15:07.43,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.47,0:15:10.14,Default,,0,0,0,,說起來昨天
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.64,0:15:13.56,Default,,0,0,0,,我去探望松本老師了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.22,0:15:14.77,Default,,0,0,0,,然後呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.02,0:15:18.14,Default,,0,0,0,,週末應該就出院了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.48,0:15:20.31,Default,,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.90,0:15:23.98,Default,,0,0,0,,老師的情況如何
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.48,0:15:25.28,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼說呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.86,0:15:27.65,Default,,0,0,0,,雖然老師面帶笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.82,0:15:30.74,Default,,0,0,0,,有時候卻看起來非常勞累
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.08,0:15:33.03,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.16,0:15:38.92,Default,,0,0,0,,老師他老人家究竟多大年紀了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.00,0:15:44.42,Default,,0,0,0,,從外表上看  這十四年來幾乎沒有變化
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.55,0:15:46.34,Default,,0,0,0,,確實
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.34,0:15:49.68,Default,,0,0,0,,就算告訴我老師已經90有餘了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.47,0:15:53.35,Default,,0,0,0,,或者還只有68歲
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.60,0:15:54.47,Default,,0,0,0,,我都能接受
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.85,0:15:55.68,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.35,0:15:58.77,Default,,0,0,0,,為了什麼奉獻一生的人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.44,0:16:02.65,Default,,0,0,0,,大概都有種遺世而獨立的氣質吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.28,0:16:08.24,Default,,0,0,0,,小光你也一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.78,0:16:10.41,Default,,0,0,0,,光陰似箭  你卻一點沒變
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.66,0:16:16.49,Default,,0,0,0,,你也是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.41,0:16:22.46,Default,,0,0,0,,初次見面以來  你也沒變過
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.80,0:16:31.59,Default,,0,0,0,,路上小心
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.72,0:16:33.51,Default,,0,0,0,,我出門了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.56,0:16:41.44,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼樣  馬締
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.94,0:16:44.52,Default,,0,0,0,,設計無可挑剔
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.52,0:16:45.52,Default,,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.65,0:16:48.11,Default,,0,0,0,,那麼接下來各部門都要開始行動了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.57,0:16:50.49,Default,,0,0,0,,拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.24,0:16:54.41,Default,,0,0,0,,我就覺得馬締先生一定會喜歡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.62,0:16:56.99,Default,,0,0,0,,哪裡  確實非常優秀
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.02,0:17:22.85,Default,,0,0,0,,完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.90,0:17:24.77,Default,,0,0,0,,沒有問題
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.85,0:17:25.52,Default,,0,0,0,,太…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.52,0:17:26.48,Default,,0,0,0,,還沒完呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.03,0:17:31.78,Default,,0,0,0,,這邊也沒有問題
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.79,0:17:49.25,Default,,0,0,0,,沒有問題
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.76,0:17:55.09,Default,,0,0,0,,所有核對工作就此結束
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.89,0:17:59.35,Default,,0,0,0,,各位辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.14,0:18:02.06,Default,,0,0,0,,太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.85,0:18:04.14,Default,,0,0,0,,恭喜
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.98,0:18:07.77,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.36,0:18:09.19,Default,,0,0,0,,你做得很好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.77,0:18:10.86,Default,,0,0,0,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.24,0:18:15.32,Default,,0,0,0,,馬締先生
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.32,0:18:18.87,Default,,0,0,0,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.95,0:18:19.91,Default,,0,0,0,,你也是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.99,0:18:24.79,Default,,0,0,0,,我一開始覺得這工作一點也不起眼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.21,0:18:26.96,Default,,0,0,0,,但我很享受
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.04,0:18:28.71,Default,,0,0,0,,是…是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.29,0:18:31.34,Default,,0,0,0,,還有需要幫忙的地方請叫上我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.75,0:18:32.96,Default,,0,0,0,,也叫上我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.55,0:18:35.05,Default,,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.59,0:18:36.34,Default,,0,0,0,,恭喜
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.34,0:18:37.22,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.22,0:18:38.14,Default,,0,0,0,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.14,0:18:38.97,Default,,0,0,0,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.05,0:18:40.05,Default,,0,0,0,,我先走了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.06,0:18:42.56,Default,,0,0,0,,剩下的工作請加油
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.02,0:18:44.14,Default,,0,0,0,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.23,0:18:51.32,Default,,0,0,0,,我真的遇到了一群優秀的兼職人員啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.07,0:18:53.69,Default,,0,0,0,,還沒結束呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.03,0:18:54.40,Default,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.57,0:18:55.65,Default,,0,0,0,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.07,0:18:58.36,Default,,0,0,0,,回去路上小心
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.36,0:18:59.74,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道了  謝謝關心
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.58,0:19:03.33,Default,,0,0,0,,大家辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.45,0:19:05.33,Default,,0,0,0,,我聽兼職的人說了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.62,0:19:08.58,Default,,0,0,0,,沒有其它遺漏的詞條
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.13,0:19:10.92,Default,,0,0,0,,可喜可賀
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.42,0:19:13.71,Default,,0,0,0,,這簡直是大家澎湃的血潮…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.71,0:19:14.71,Default,,0,0,0,,搞什麼  西岡
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.88,0:19:17.22,Default,,0,0,0,,最近也不見你的人影
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.22,0:19:18.13,Default,,0,0,0,,現在來幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.26,0:19:20.43,Default,,0,0,0,,啊  您好過分啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.10,0:19:26.43,Default,,0,0,0,,我也在用自己的方式為『大渡海』拚命工作
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.19,0:19:28.94,Default,,0,0,0,,證據就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.40,0:19:31.48,Default,,0,0,0,,看好了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.23,0:19:35.86,Default,,0,0,0,,『大渡海』的吉祥物  名字是「小海」
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.70,0:19:41.49,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼樣  可愛吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.70,0:19:43.16,Default,,0,0,0,,是的  非常可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.33,0:19:45.41,Default,,0,0,0,,這是什麼東西啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.75,0:19:48.18,Default,,0,0,0,,西岡人不怎麼樣  品味卻不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.25,0:19:49.58,Default,,0,0,0,,喂  連佐佐木姐也挖苦我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.71,0:19:51.04,Default,,0,0,0,,好過分哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.81,0:20:21.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn@方正中雅宋_GBK\frz270\fs35\bord0\b0\fade(700,1000)\pos(579,127)}【驕傲】
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.31,0:20:21.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn@方正中雅宋_GBK\frz270\fs35\bord0\b0\fade(700,1000)\pos(505,185)}自豪。自尊心。
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.31,0:20:21.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn@方正中雅宋_GBK\frz270\fs35\bord0\b0\fade(700,1000)\pos(455,232)}「獻身於事業之人的～」
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.45,0:21:44.95,Default,,0,0,0,,天氣真好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.36,0:21:47.32,Default,,0,0,0,,奶奶您坐好了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.41,0:21:49.37,Default,,0,0,0,,突然間這是怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.70,0:21:51.12,Default,,0,0,0,,大家一起照個相吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.37,0:21:52.50,Default,,0,0,0,,小光  快過來
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.75,0:21:54.33,Default,,0,0,0,,好的
